name: Nobody's Here (Pareal Games)
description:
Welcome to the Lonliest Place on the Entire Planet, where you won't find anything there, just yourself.

 Leave a Review from one of Our A4 Paper Sheets and Put it on the Ground, to remind people of how great it is when they first enter.

Controls:

Move: WASD

Interact: LMB (Left Mouse Button)

Music and Sound Effects (aside from man on radio) from Zapsplat.com
